# AFTER MAKING ANY CHANGES HERE, MAKE SURE TO RESTART THE API AND THEN RELOAD THE WEB UI PAGE (you do not need to restart it) FOR THEM TO APPLY

HOST="0.0.0.0" # IP you want the API to run on. 0.0.0.0 is automatically set to YOURS and needs no configuration.
PORT="8080"    # Port you want the API to use. 8080 is standard.

